articles.title: ‘Leader’ Damian Priest Welcomes JD McDonagh To The Judgment Day, Lineup For Next Week’s RAW - eWrestlingNews
articles.description: JD McDonagh is finally part of The Judgment Day, being accepted into the faction on this week's episode of Monday Night RAW.
articles.content:
Damian Priest proclaimed himself as the leader of The Judgment Day on Monday Night RAW, which startled his fellow stablemates.
